seo: 富通天下,外贸ERP,任意文件上传,漏洞检测
seo_en: Futong ERP, foreign trade ERP, arbitrary file upload, vulnerability detection
summary: 该插件用于检测富通天下-外贸ERP系统中的任意文件上传漏洞，通过构造特定请求验证是否存在该漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect arbitrary file upload vulnerabilities in the Futong foreign trade ERP system by constructing specific requests to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
